snippet.title: Trace Hunters | May 2024 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Looking for the latest trailer? Check it out here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dTk7K7N9kp4

Trace Hunters is a third-person shooter where you pilot a futuristic combat vehicle. Outnumbered and alone, blast through hordes of enemies to discover precious resources and traces of lost technology. Unlock new weapons to take on even greater challenges! 

Wishlist on Steam today!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2706210?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=gameplay-trailer
